See http://www.plugpbx.org

PlugPBX is a pre-built image you can boot your SheevaPlug and have a full featured PBX phone system.

Based On:

 * Debian Linux
 * Asterisk
 * FreePBX
 * Webmin

These are intended as build scripts to take a stock Debian booting SheevaPlug and setup/install/build
a standard PlugPBX system automatically. Its will a work in progress. 

Look for tagged releases or branches later on, or feel free to pitch in. 


